  "detailed_description": "Non Fingo is a VR Space Combat Sim with n-body gravity, realistic(ish) physics, fully simulated projectiles, and 0g player movement in Early Access under active development by an independent, solo developer. Though it's starting as a wave defense-in-orbit game, it has room to expand to a multiplayer ship crew galaxy-scale adventure game. Join me in our discord server to help steer development!",
